## Appearance settings:

set font "monospace regular 13"

# Set background and bar colors
set default-bg "#473d4b"
set statusbar-bg "#473d4b"
set inputbar-bg "#473d4b"
set inputbar-fg "#f9c1c4"

set incremental-search

# Set space between pages
# set page-padding 10



## Key mappings:

map u scroll half-up
map d scroll half-down

map r reload
map R rotate

map - zoom out
map = zoom in
map + zoom reset

map i recolor
